"title": "5569: suffering, hardship",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5569: suffering, hardship",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture provides examples of types of hardship which people may expect to encounter.</p>\n<h2>Different kinds of hardship</h2>\n<h3>Poverty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:15\">PRO 10:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:11\">DEU 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:5-Job24:11\">JOB 24:5–24:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:11\">MAT 26:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:7\">MRK 14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:8\">JHN 12:8</a></p>\n<h3>Hunger and thirst</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:4-Ps107:5\">PSA 107:4–107:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:53-Gen41:57\">GEN 41:53–41:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:22-Exod15:24\">EXO 15:22–15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:2-Exod16:3\">EXO 16:2–16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:1-Exod17:3\">EXO 17:1–17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:4-Num11:6\">NUM 11:4–11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:7-1Kgs17:12\">1KI 17:7–17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:1-Neh5:5\">NEH 5:1–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:2\">MAT 4:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:2\">LUK 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>Hard labour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:38-Gen31:42\">GEN 31:38–31:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:3-2Chr10:4\">2CH 10:3–10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:21-Eccl2:22\">ECC 2:21–2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:9\">1TH 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Oppression</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job35:9\">JOB 35:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11\">EXO 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:23\">EXO 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:8-Exod5:9\">EXO 5:8–5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:1\">2KI 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:5\">PSA 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:13\">PSA 31:9–31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:1\">ECC 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:6\">JER 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:9\">AMO 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>Danger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:21-Neh4:23\">NEH 4:21–4:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:8\">EXO 18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:26\">1KI 2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:15-1Chr11:19\">1CH 11:15–11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:27-Acts27:44\">ACT 27:27–27:44</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those who suffered hardship</h2>\n<h3>Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:47-Deut28:48\">DEU 28:47–28:48</a></strong> <em>God's people suffered under his chastisement.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:15\">DEU 8:15</a> <em>their suffering in the wilderness</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:6-Deut26:7\">DEU 26:6–26:7</a> <em>their suffering in Egypt</em></p>\n<h3>David was oppressed by his enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:1\">PSA 132:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Paul suffered in serving the Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:4-2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:4–6:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God's people must endure hardship</h2>\n<h3>The example of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a></p>\n<h3>The suffering of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:21-Acts14:22\">ACT 14:21–14:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:11-1Cor4:13\">1CO 4:11–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:8-2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:8–1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:23–11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:11-Phil4:14\">PHP 4:11–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:3\">2TI 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:34\">HEB 10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:37-Heb11:38\">HEB 11:37–11:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7\">HEB 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:3\">REV 2:3</a></p>\n<h3>The need for faith, courage and endurance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:6\">HEB 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:36\">HEB 10:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:9\">REV 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:12\">REV 14:12</a></p>\n<h2>God helps his people through hardship</h2>\n<h3>He provides for them</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:16\">DEU 8:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:2-1Kgs17:9\">1KI 17:2–17:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:19\">PHP 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:19\">PHP 4:19</a></p>\n<h3>He comforts them with his love</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:4\">2CO 1:3–1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a></p>\n<h3>He sets heaven before them</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16-Rev7:17\">REV 7:16–7:17</a></p>",
